<h2 class="section-heading">Guiding Principles</h2>
<p>At St Francis Girls Suwerwa, every decision we make and every student we shape is anchored in our Motto, Vision, Mission and Core Values. Together they define who we are, what we do, and why we do it.</p>

<!-- MOTTO: called out on its own since it's the school's single guiding phrase -->
<div class="commitment-quote">
  Our Motto: "<strong>Strive For Excellence</strong>"
</div>

<div class="mvv-grid">
  <div class="mvv-card">
    <span class="mvv-icon"></span>
    <h3>Our Vision</h3>
    <p>To Be a Leading Institution in Academic Excellence.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="mvv-card featured">
    <span class="mvv-icon"></span>
    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
    <p>To Provide Quality Education By Nurturing Innovativeness, Responsiveness, Integrity And Moral Christian Values In Learners Who Will Contribute Positively Towards National Development.</p>
  </div>
  <!-- mvv-card-wide spans the full grid width so all 10 pills have room -->
  <div class="mvv-card mvv-card-wide">
    <span class="mvv-icon"></span>
    <h3>Core Values</h3>
    <div class="values-row">
      <span class="value-pill">God Fearing</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Integrity</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Team Work</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Courtesy</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Efficiency</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Continued Improvement</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Professionalism</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Confidentiality</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Fidelity to Law</span>
      <span class="value-pill">Respect For Individual Differences</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
